This software is an Eclipse/OSGi plugin for 1C:EDT. It is built against, and runs
inside, 1C:EDT, using the Eclipse Platform and 1C:EDT plugin APIs (their respective
licenses apply). At runtime it uses Google Gson (Apache License 2.0). Those
dependencies are provided by the host EDT environment and are not redistributed by
this project.
